{"tid":1460521,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三跑地盤推土機失控連人墮海 操作員送院後證實不治","createTime":"2019-08-13T03:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T08:30:57.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8efb1cac68ed4965590377441a47db1d1cf65a","tid":1460521,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:22:26.000Z","msg":"機場三跑地盤遇奪命意外，好爸爸喪命遺妻及三年幼子女！一名推土機操作員，昨第三日在赤鱲角機場第三條跑道地盤進行填海工程，疑在近海邊泥坡褪機時，推土機突然失控，連人帶機墮坡翻入海中沉沒，地盤潛水員迅速落水搜救，十五分鐘後將他救起，但事主已陷入昏迷，送院後證實不治。死者生前是家庭經濟支柱，遺孀及三名年幼子女頓感徬徨無助。警方將案件列作工業意外，勞工處已向地盤發出暫時停工通知書，將進一步調查意外成因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190813/00176_038.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190813%2F00176_038.html&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9xD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=27f5e1dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190813/00176_038.html</a>"},{"pid":"185061f7cd11d149d9957bf7f540101def28617e","tid":1460521,"uid":98022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943fb80844a4e1dd7cb5b6f616af53c625fab81e","tid":1460521,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"好慘<br />\n有冇基金"},{"pid":"fc78be450f4ab67e9beaaf728a26ff439e7dc1c5","tid":1460521,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:55:21.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">遺孀及三名年幼子女頓感徬徨無助</code></pre><br />\n喪親竟非哀傷，而係徬惶"},{"pid":"3a1a50eaa52b53b39fa4fb2165a5289085983e07","tid":1460521,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" c